snippet.title: Gamma-Goblins for the Apple II
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

Gamma-Goblins is a shoot'em-up in which you destroy hostile aliens and bombs.


What I think:

It's not horrible, but I don't like it anyways. So repetitive and when does the next wave of enemies come? 

Obviously NEVER!
